    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_3",
      "block_index": 3,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "character_list",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "柳金蝉：旦",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_4",
      "block_index": 4,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "情节",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 2,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_5",
      "block_index": 5,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "宋仁宗大放花灯，与民同乐。有女子柳金蝉随家人逛灯中途失散，踽踽独行，被无赖李保诱至家中，强奸逼死，移尸颜查散门首卸祸。地方不察，逮颜查散于案。包拯审问时，颜查散极口呼冤。包拯以颜查散书生，",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 94,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_6",
      "block_index": 6,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "不类杀人者，乃下阴曹，令判官查生死簿。簿上注明柳金蝉因看灯为颜查散奸毙。包拯终不信，私访至阴山，",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 48,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_7",
      "block_index": 7,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "得柳金蝉冤魂而问之，始知凶手为李保，而判官为李保之母舅，徇私舞弊，擅改生死簿。包拯大怒，立令判官改正。判官不认，竞至与阎罗相骂，包拯怒铡之。回至阳世，释颜查散，铡李保了案。",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 86,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_8",
      "block_index": 8,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "根据《戏考》第二册整理",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_9",
      "block_index": 9,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "扶大宋锦华夷赤心肝胆，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "内二黄导板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_10",
      "block_index": 10,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（包拯上，四青袍、王朝、马汉、张龙、赵虎同上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 24,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_11",
      "block_index": 11,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "坐开封无一日心不忧烦。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "回龙"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_12",
      "block_index": 12,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "多只为那柳金蝉屈死凄惨，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_13",
      "block_index": 13,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "错断了颜查散年幼儿男。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_14",
      "block_index": 14,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "我且到望乡台亲自查看，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_15",
      "block_index": 15,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（包拯上台子。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_16",
      "block_index": 16,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "又只见：大鬼卒、小鬼判、牛头马面，押定了去世的亡魂项带铁链，悲惨惨，阴风绕，遍体冷，我心胆皆寒。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 34,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄垛板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_18",
      "block_index": 18,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "站立在望乡台用目观看：",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_19",
      "block_index": 19,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "望开封那就是自己的家园。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_20",
      "block_index": 20,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "牙床上睡一人蓬头铁面，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_21",
      "block_index": 21,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "有王朝和马汉睡卧在两边。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_22",
      "block_index": 22,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "可怜他初为官定远小县，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_23",
      "block_index": 23,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "可怜他审赵大又被人参。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_24",
      "block_index": 24,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "可怜他断日光又把君谏，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_25",
      "block_index": 25,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "可怜他为查散，下阴曹，游七殿，一殿一殿哪得安然！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 24,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_26",
      "block_index": 26,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "观东方一阵明一阵发暗，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_27",
      "block_index": 27,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "那就是受罪处名叫阴山。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_28",
      "block_index": 28,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "屈死鬼一定在那厢受难，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_29",
      "block_index": 29,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "俺包拯要入那虎穴龙潭。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_30",
      "block_index": 30,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "叫王朝，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 4,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_31",
      "block_index": 31,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_王朝",
      "text": "有。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "王朝",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_32",
      "block_index": 32,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "和马汉，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 4,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_33",
      "block_index": 33,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_马汉",
      "text": "有。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "马汉",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_34",
      "block_index": 34,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "阴山去看，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄原板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_35",
      "block_index": 35,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（包拯下台子。油流鬼上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 13,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_36",
      "block_index": 36,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "何方冤鬼，少往前进！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 10,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_37",
      "block_index": 37,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "唔！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_38",
      "block_index": 38,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "山谷中缘何有一鬼孤单？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_39",
      "block_index": 39,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "何方冤鬼，在此摆来摆去？待我油流鬼将你们拿下！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 23,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_40",
      "block_index": 40,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "唔，你为何叫做油流鬼？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_41",
      "block_index": 41,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "各殿灯油，多是我添，故而叫做油流鬼。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 18,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_42",
      "block_index": 42,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "你在此作甚？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_43",
      "block_index": 43,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "在此看守冤鬼。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_44",
      "block_index": 44,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "唔，你这里也有冤鬼么？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_45",
      "block_index": 45,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "冤鬼多得很，你问他干什么？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 13,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_46",
      "block_index": 46,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "哦，老夫就是那龙图阁大学士兼理开封，包拯。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 21,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_47",
      "block_index": 47,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "原来是包大人，小鬼不知，多有得罪！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 17,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_48",
      "block_index": 48,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "罢了，起来。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_49",
      "block_index": 49,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "多谢大人！不在阳间来到阴山作甚？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_50",
      "block_index": 50,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "老夫只为一桩奇冤，亲下阴曹。你在此看守，多是些什么冤鬼？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 28,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_51",
      "block_index": 51,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "内有一女鬼，名叫柳氏金蝉。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 13,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_52",
      "block_index": 52,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "那柳金蝉……",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_53",
      "block_index": 53,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "正是。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_54",
      "block_index": 54,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "得何病症而死？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_55",
      "block_index": 55,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "因李保图财害命，用绳索勒死的。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 15,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_56",
      "block_index": 56,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "这就不对了。老夫在五殿也曾看过生死簿：“颜查散谋死表妹柳金蝉”，怎么说是李保？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 39,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_57",
      "block_index": 57,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "你要说颜查散谋害人命，这就屈枉死好人！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 19,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_58",
      "block_index": 58,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "怎见得？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 4,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_59",
      "block_index": 59,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "那旁有一太湖石，你且坐下，待我慢慢儿的讲来。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 22,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_60",
      "block_index": 60,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "慢慢讲来。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_61",
      "block_index": 61,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "只因正月十五日大放花灯，忽然狂风一阵，将灯吹灭。来了一只猛虎，将柳小姐背到喜鹊桥边。来了恶人李保，图财害命，用绳索勒死的。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 61,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_62",
      "block_index": 62,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "那柳金蝉为何不到阎君那里控告于他？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 17,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_63",
      "block_index": 63,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "想她前去控告，那李保乃是我家判爷的外甥，将柳小姐藏在阴山，将生死簿改移了“颜查散谋死表妹柳金蝉”。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 49,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_64",
      "block_index": 64,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "他改移生死簿难道上面无有墨迹么？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_65",
      "block_index": 65,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "他撕了一篇，写上一篇，哪里来的墨迹！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 18,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_66",
      "block_index": 66,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "他撕了一篇，放在何处？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_67",
      "block_index": 67,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "他揉了纸揉，订了生死簿。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_68",
      "block_index": 68,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "你待怎讲？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_69",
      "block_index": 69,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "订了生死簿。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_70",
      "block_index": 70,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "好判官！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 4,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_71",
      "block_index": 71,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "好一个大胆无知判官，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 10,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_72",
      "block_index": 72,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "改移了生死簿讲我遮瞒。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_73",
      "block_index": 73,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "五阎君依仗你是阴曹的障暗，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 13,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_74",
      "block_index": 74,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "油流鬼有一事还要你仔细详参。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_75",
      "block_index": 75,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "油流鬼，柳金蝉的阴魂今在何处？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 15,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_76",
      "block_index": 76,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "现在阴山背后石桥底下。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_77",
      "block_index": 77,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "带路，老夫观看。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_78",
      "block_index": 78,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "待我唤她一声，听她讲些什么。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 14,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_79",
      "block_index": 79,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "但凭于你。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_80",
      "block_index": 80,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "柳金蝉，阎君查看阴山，你可要听好了！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 18,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_81",
      "block_index": 81,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_柳金蝉",
      "text": "苦吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "柳金蝉",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "内白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_82",
      "block_index": 82,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_柳金蝉",
      "text": "在阳间哪知道阴世路远，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "柳金蝉",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "内二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_83",
      "block_index": 83,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_柳金蝉",
      "text": "柳金蝉这冤仇总有万千。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "柳金蝉",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_84",
      "block_index": 84,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_柳金蝉",
      "text": "那判爷与李保骨肉亲眷，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "柳金蝉",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_85",
      "block_index": 85,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_柳金蝉",
      "text": "但不知何日里得见青天？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "柳金蝉",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_86",
      "block_index": 86,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "你听见没有？",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_87",
      "block_index": 87,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "嗳！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_88",
      "block_index": 88,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "耳听得哭声高如同眼见，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_89",
      "block_index": 89,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "方信那油流鬼话不虚传。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_90",
      "block_index": 90,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_包拯",
      "text": "带上了柳金蝉老夫判断，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "包拯",
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_91",
      "block_index": 91,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_油流鬼",
      "text": "我家判爷厉害！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 7,
      "speaker_name_raw": "油流鬼",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_92",
      "block_index": 92,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "dialogue",
